task.summary:
This is a big one.
<+> Updated all utilities to include documentation for the future API <+> Updated RepariforsAction <+> Changed "Main" to "HPChatPlugin" in preparation for the future API <+> Updated most files to reflect the change of the main class <+> Updated boss bar task to change the color of itself and the messages based on your house <+> Changed how the command, PM, and chat logs work to create a new file for each day <+> Added TimeExtensionTask.java to double the time of the day/night cycle <+> Began writing the more robust HPPlayer.java <+> Began working on player settings (shift-click) <+> Began working on mail system <+> Added ItemBuilder.java for faster item creation <+> Added ProtocolLib as a dependency for the plugin.yml <+> Added configuration options for house points (not implemented) <+> Added more robust configuration options for the boss bar
